      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED AURA (5) jumped well from a low draw and lead for much way to score when second (22.92) at The Gardens in a Grade 5 over 400m. Likely to feature again. LIMITLESS LARSON (8) finished second (22.43) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th at The Gardens. Has a good record here at this journey. Can figure in the finish. GINNY RIGGS (1) has good early dash but last time was shuffled out the back and missed the frame, finishing eighth (23.16) in a Grade 4/5 at Bulli. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Likely to be thereabouts. FASCINATE ABBY (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
